text:
Saint West Cannot Deal in This Photo with Santa and North West's Reaction Is Priceless 
This is one for the photo album. Most Popular By Sarah Lindig Jan 14, 2017 It's all too common for parents, expecting an adorable smiley picture for their holiday card, to end up with one of their toddler screaming as he or she sits on Santa Claus' lap. Even Saint West was in hysterics when he met Saint Nick. Kim Kardashian shared this photo of her two children meeting Santa Claus on her app: KimKardashian.com Advertisement - Continue Reading Below While Saint expresses his discontentment with the situation, the funniest part of the photo is North's reaction to her younger brother's utter lack of chill. She may be all calm and collected now, but it wasn't too long ago that North herself was a little reticent about the old man in red... A photo posted by Kim Kardashian West (@kimkardashian) on Dec 26, 2014 at 7:34pm PST Don't worry, Saint. Next year will be better. More from ELLE:
